#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cvendor-tab-implementation.md:117
msgid "Certification auto-population"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cvendor-tab-implementation.md:119
msgid ""
"The Vendor tab watches the Organisation tab's identifier and automatically "
"populates `vendorService.certification.certifiedBy` with the competent "
"authority URI:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cvendor-tab-implementation.md:121
msgid ""
"useEffect(() => {\n"
"  if (organization.identifier) {\n"
"    const orgUri = organization.identifier.startsWith('http')\n"
"      ? organization.identifier\n"
"      : `https://regels.overheid.nl/organizations/${organization.identifier}"
"`;\n"
"    setVendorService(prev => ({\n"
"      ...prev,\n"
"      certification: { ...prev.certification, certifiedBy: orgUri }\n"
"    }));\n"
"  }\n"
"}, [organization.identifier]);"
msgstr ""

